"A.P.241/10/15/11:00": "Phew, was it just me or... Did the enemies feel really strong today..."
"Hehehe. That is probably, very likely, the answer and not just your imagination."
"Yes, it's Lisa, hello! This must have been quite the mission if it required two Guardians on a sortie together."
"Oh, we were on the bridge together, so... But never mind that, you said it wasn't just my imagination?"
"The enemies of course. To describe them, they were strong and tough."
"Lisa shoots and shoots and shoots all kinds of Darkers, so she knows."
"These ones that that just appeared were different. They were stronger, and tougher, and stranger."
"And the alarms happened to be slow to respond to this level of invasion."
"Now, why couldn't anyone predict this attack?"
"Lisa only knows what happened. The enemy's strength was unusual, and our response was unusual too. That's all Lisa knows."
"Well, Lisa is off to find more of those strange Darkers to play with. Ehehe, hehehehehe."
"<%me>, Matoi, the situation seems to be all clear now. Could you please return back to the bridge?"
